 Apocalypse nodded to Neptune as they watched the pod
crash. Neptune sped off at great speed.aw he had been
beated to the new bot already but landed down anyway.
"My name is Neptune. Soilder of the destrons. My
leader would like to meet you. Would you like to meet
him our base is this way. Youve been through a lot we
have a base and im certain we can give you a quarters
to sleep in while you recover from your ordeal."
